# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
Just iterate from back instead of from front. Then keep adding and handling carry variable.
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Just add as if adding a normal numbers
Like if you want to add 239 + 1 then first you do 9+1 = 10, then we take 0 and carry 1.
This 0 above is 10%10 and 1 is 10/10. Thus, I have taken, digits[i] = add%10 and carry is add/10.


At the end if the carry is not 0 --> Add an element in the vector at the frontend.
Ex - 9 + 1 = 0 and carry 1
So insert it at the beginning as 10 to make 9+1=10
