Thought about how we can minimize the amount of computation.

# Approach
Loop backward. 

1. In case of 9, assign 0. That means we need to increment next digit.
2. The others increment and return the digits. 
3. If the loop has been finished, that means, it requres additional digit. add it and return it.

Only the 3 cases requires additional Memory space and breaks before reach N.

