Solution : 
For generating unique difference between subsequent elements we have to generate elements in a zig zag manner

for n = 6  -> 1, 6, 2, 5, 3, 4 

No we want only k < n unique difference between subsequent elements.
For this we generate same difference between subsqeuent elements n - k times and then generate k unique difference between subsequent elements from there on.

