Keep last n - k values as they should be. ⇒ generating consecutive difference of 1
Fill from k'th element to 1st element by alternately picking from increasing direction (1 to k) and decreasing direction (k to 1). ⇒ generating consecutive difference of k, k - 1, ... 3, 2, 1

