	if (scd[0]+1)<0:
		heapq.heappush(hp, (scd[0]+1, scd[1]))
if hp and hp[0][0]<-1:
	return ""
else:
	if hp and hp[0][0]==-1:
		return ans+hp[0][1]
	else:
		return ans
```

