# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
- Storing frequencies
- check if max freq is greater than half of length+1 , if it is we cannot form alternating different characters
- adding freqs and respective chars in maxheap such that we can get the alternating chars easily. 


# Code
```
class Solution {
public:
    string reorganizeString(string s) {
        int l = s.length();
        unordered_map<char,int> um;
        for(auto it : s)
            um[it]+=1;
        int maxi = 0;

        priority_queue<pair<int,char>> pq;
        for(auto it : um){
            maxi = max(maxi,it.second);
            pq.push({it.second,it.first});
        }

        if(maxi > (l+1)/2)
            return "";

        string res;

        while(pq.size()){
            auto ptr = pq.top();
            pq.pop();
            res+=ptr.second;

            if(pq.size()){
                auto ptr2 = pq.top();
                pq.pop();
                res+=ptr2.second;


                if(ptr2.first>1)
                    pq.push({ptr2.first-1,ptr2.second});
            }

            if(ptr.first>1)
                pq.push({ptr.first-1,ptr.second});

        }
        return res;

    }
};
```

